Explicit liber de incendio amoris. Hic incipiunt uerba difficilia per diuersos doctores exposita que continentur in libro qui uocatur melum Ricardi heremite. (ff. 84—84b contains 41 words from Abrogare-Defecare, the end of the list being missing.
